Our experiments compare against several baselines, including LLM-based ranking.
We focus on the book domain, using slices of datasets from Amazon and Goodreads, where we select users with long review text (see Table (ref) for dataset statistics).
Code and data are available at {\small\url{https://personalization.mpi-inf.mpg.de/CUP}}.